        <abstract> 
<p>Would like to see essay [on effects of conscription in France, see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">10774</hi>]. Knows of Swiss memoir to the same effect. Author says Swiss yeomen apt to leave homestead to sickly son. Landed populations deteriorate.</p> 
        </abstract>
